name: Jawa68
content:
"Jawa68" was the online alias of a Jawa who spent time on Tatooine. By 0 BBY, Jawa68 encountered Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina's policy of not allowing Jawas, which Jawa68 found annoying. Jawa68 posted a one-star review of the cantina in Yoda's Guide to the Galaxy, a book written by the Jedi Master Yoda during his exile on Dagobah.
Jawa68 was mentioned in the 2021 non-canon reference book LEGO Star Wars Yoda's Galaxy Atlas.
